@startuml
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
boundary "System" as System


== Register Storage Area ==
Officer -> System : Submit new StorageArea(type, location, maxCapacity, occupancy, docks?, distances?)
System --> Officer : Confirmation (StorageAreaDto with Id)

== Update Storage Area ==
Officer -> System : Submit update StorageArea(id, type?, location?, capacity?, occupancy?, docks?, distances?)
System --> Officer : Confirmation (Updated StorageAreaDto)

== Validation ==
Officer -> System : Attempt register/update with occupancy > capacity
System --> Officer : Error (BusinessRuleValidationException)

== Query ==
Officer -> System : Request details of StorageArea(id)
System --> Officer : StorageAreaDto

@enduml
